    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款以<strong>悬疑、冒险、智斗</strong>为主题的<strong>长篇视觉小说</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个在妖怪环伺下封闭了千年的古老村庄，正接连发生着诡异的妖怪杀人事件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与天斗、与地斗、与人斗，在善与恶的交锋中开辟。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/2b0620d469cbee8c7b5084dec03d936a.poster.avif?t=1772165776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/2b0620d469cbee8c7b5084dec03d936a.webm?t=1772165776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/2b0620d469cbee8c7b5084dec03d936a.mp4?t=1772165776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>神秘祭典，古怪政局，真言咒诅，神木天成，表面的古井不波，背后究竟藏着什么样的真相，等待你的揭露与见证。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/e1b2c2c2f7f9ad2e7435f9bc6f64ed31.poster.avif?t=1772165776\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/e1b2c2c2f7f9ad2e7435f9bc6f64ed31.webm?t=1772165776\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/e1b2c2c2f7f9ad2e7435f9bc6f64ed31.mp4?t=1772165776\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325310/extras/bcf58ba863ec58735ee0f6c84fa8366e.poster.avif?t=1772165776\" wi